text: This facade is a must see, old guard dress in olden times are maching and guarding the place. They are very accommodating in having selfie with everyone...no entrance fee..
My friends enjoyed the photo taken Namdaemoon (Soongraemoon) background , one of the 4 main gates of Old Seoul. It is good to visit.

This attraction was near the hotel so we went to check it out.It's small, only the gate left but it's very ancient and preserved with great care.The guards with the swords are just so cool thing to see.
